>\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2387299\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2387299&d=RjdfG9uxtkM%2FelS3aO62sCIHZ%2BXcjpWsQ0IfaGt1pN0%3D&h=fb44a8ee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2387299</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T02:59:34.000Z","msg":"班人都唔係我選出來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da70908f19dc2acc0f43c9e161497c0c3ab4f063","tid":2489381,"uid":292424,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T03:05:44.000Z","msg":"不過又真係冇曬示威遊行<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 駁唔到 <br />\n不過你條大陸仔阻唔到我地食黃店<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09115dececc3bd1b4f4de0ad9f87a179729a8ae6","tid":2489381,"uid":173817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T03:07:11.000Z","msg":"打多d la岩la活係自己幻想"},{"pid":"e795c0d102659000f5f3391cb55ee52a9c3de491","tid":2489381,"uid":128334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T03:08:23.000Z","msg":"繼續打飛機呃藍屍就岩啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d7a251e3370eaeb546128c47a6c08a20f087e4a","tid":2489381,"uid":121197,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"44610f93e8e2f2a3eedbaab5db796ae7eb92de85","tid":2489381,"uid":266131,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T02:47:14.000Z","msg":"Abouthai 件事政府應該好嬲<br />\n<br />\n知道市民係心不服"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T03:08:54.000Z","msg":"心不服又如何<br />\n共產黨都無當過香港人係人<br />\n總之要你跪"},{"pid":"424d1dc3407169e32bc5712980e4ae79792cb1a4","tid":2489381,"uid":242677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5d7a251e3370eaeb546128c47a6c08a20f087e4a","tid":2489381,"uid":121197,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"44610f93e8e2f2a3eedbaab5db796ae7eb92de85","tid":2489381,"uid":266131,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T02:47:1